# Online Shopping Website

This is a basic frontend e-commerce website built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

##  Features
- Product listing interface
- Simple "Add to Cart" interaction
- Clean and responsive layout
- User-friendly design

## Technologies Used
- HTML
- CSS
- JavaScript

##  Live Demo
https://hassannn434.github.io/online-shop

##  Learning Outcome
- Understanding of frontend web development
- UI design basics
- JavaScript interaction handling
